| logical_plan  | Filter: tvmaze.request_path = Utf8("/shows/169") OR tvmaze.request_path = Utf8("/search/people") AND tvmaze.request_query = Utf8("q=michael")                                                                                  |
|               |   TableScan: tvmaze projection=[request_path, request_query, content], partial_filters=[tvmaze.request_path = Utf8("/shows/169") OR tvmaze.request_path = Utf8("/search/people") AND tvmaze.request_query = Utf8("q=michael")] |
| physical_plan | CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                                                                                                                    |
